{"tid":230100,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"返左幾日工已經唔想返是咪失敗","createTime":"2017-05-05T06:13:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T13:51:57.000Z","uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4482711381dc510b3840e2188db6afc613947594","tid":230100,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:13:37.000Z","msg":"中學畢業就已經返緊工<br />\n不過係垃圾pt 黎<br />\n唔算好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n跟住個心仲想玩<br />\n所以一抖就抖左半年有多<br />\n有朋友介紹就去左返工<br />\n咁返左幾日真係好撚攰<br />\n係個心未返黎定已經玩厭左<br />\n<br />\n琴日已經交左信<br />\n想搵錢又唔辛苦既工香港其實有冇"},{"pid":"cf7f848c0b531a314fd96d73bcb5e73d77df6573","tid":230100,"uid":94457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:14:59.000Z","msg":"有 收租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過要父幹 你有無先？<br />\n無就努力返工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c739dc63bbe25aa99662fa5e8944d47913b51a5c","tid":230100,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:16:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有 收租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過要父幹 你有無先？<br />\n無就努力返工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係冇<br />\n唔係唔辛苦得<br />\n可能呢排發生好多野<br />\n個心都唔喺度"},{"pid":"85b9dd29274a08b853f46154a736811e686c9dbb","tid":230100,"uid":109650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:21:11.000Z","msg":"藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a04db8e2295716e201b95f8945fc860820d3e96","tid":230100,"uid":109650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:21:27.000Z","msg":"原本返咩工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e03a7095f2dc6346a18977abb65b6e7b8695e4","tid":230100,"uid":99212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:24:37.000Z","msg":"有咩工揾到錢又唔辛苦，你舉下例子先問香港有冇好冇？<br />\n<br />\n當你仲想玩，年薪幾高都係假<img src=\"/as